AUDIENCE: Yeah.

00:23:49.426 --> 00:23:50.650
[LAUGHTER]

00:23:50.650 --> 00:23:53.142
MASSIMO BOTTURA: This is--
this is something that--

00:23:53.142 --> 00:23:54.600
AUDIENCE: Who would
you stage with?

00:23:54.600 --> 00:23:56.308
MASSIMO BOTTURA: I
never work for anyone.

00:23:56.308 --> 00:23:59.060
I work for Ray [? Costantini ?]
in New York, when

00:23:59.060 --> 00:24:02.990
