00:24:02.990 --> 00:24:04.870
And it was Cafe de [? Nona ?].

00:24:04.870 --> 00:24:09.090
He was a Calabrian
guy, hairdresser.

00:24:10.140 --> 00:24:13.000
And he was giving
party to his house.

00:24:13.000 --> 00:24:15.500
And everyone would say, oh, Ray.

00:24:15.500 --> 00:24:17.440
You're so good at cooking.

00:24:17.440 --> 00:24:19.190
You just have to
open a restaurant.

00:24:19.190 --> 00:24:23.230
It was like, when I met him,
