you just, in the nose,

00:25:16.180 --> 00:25:17.970
you have red fruit.

00:25:17.970 --> 00:25:19.170
You have toasted almond.

00:25:20.330 --> 00:25:24.560
You have the old earth--
also truffles sometimes.

00:25:24.560 --> 00:25:28.730
And it's so complex
