[LAUGHTER]

00:31:47.390 --> 00:31:47.890
No.

00:31:48.930 --> 00:31:51.560
We are very lucky that
we have the opportunity

00:31:51.560 --> 00:31:54.520
to have incredible ingredients.

00:31:54.520 --> 00:31:58.430
And another thing that my
wife-- she's from New York.

00:31:58.430 --> 00:32:01.430
